460
00:36:38,757 --> 00:36:43,149
We'd like to be alone with him
for a little while, if that's okay.

461
00:36:43,358 --> 00:36:46,589
Oh, absolutely, absolutely.
Please take as much time as you need.

462
00:36:47,398 --> 00:36:49,515
Thanks.

463
00:37:12,164 --> 00:37:14,837
- Say fromage!
- Fromage.

464
00:37:16,685 --> 00:37:20,519
Hey, you were really
great today, Nate.

465
00:37:20,725 --> 00:37:23,798
Standing up to Billy.
I felt like some white-trash girl...

466
00:37:24,006 --> 00:37:26,885
...whose boyfriend
was the biggest badass in town.

467
00:37:27,087 --> 00:37:30,284
- Your brother's seriously ill, Brenda.
- Yeah, whatever.

468
00:37:30,488 --> 00:37:34,959
But you know what?
We're in faux Paris, so let's party.

469
00:39:11,869 --> 00:39:13,222
Hi.

470
00:39:13,829 --> 00:39:16,902
- I'm Amber.
- David.

471
00:39:17,110 --> 00:39:21,184
