472
00:39:21,391 --> 00:39:22,870
- I am?
- Very.

473
00:39:23,751 --> 00:39:27,301
Your friend just bought you
a lap dance with me.

474
00:39:29,793 --> 00:39:33,911
- Excuse me?
- So where you from, David?

475
00:39:34,834 --> 00:39:38,827
